Arc shape channel grid creator.   Arc length can be specified by degree with straight channel inlet nd outlet.   

v1.0.23110901　release:2023.11.9　Keita Hoshino
・Fixed the issue where iRIC would crash when the total width of the floodplain on both banks exceeded the channel width, regardless of the presence of compound channels.

v1.0.22090201　release:2022.9.2　Keita Hoshino
・Fixed a bug related to Compound Channel creation.
・Changed the specified parameters from "Right flood plane width" and "Low water channel width" to "Right flood plane width" and "Left flood plane width".
・Change to it possible to set different heights for the left and right flood plane.